Globally diversified mining company Anglo American Platinum (Amplats) and global automation and engineering solutions provider Siemens are at the forefront of rethinking how mining works with the development and implementation of digital and technological innovations, writes Sascha Solomons. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 8 2018. It will be published online on the 19th September 2018. You can read the full digital magazine here or subscribe here to receive a print copy